    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This naturally aspirated powerhouse utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to reach its 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis is equipped with an M Variable Differential Lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC), ensuring optimal torque vectoring and suspension response. Recent preventative maintenance includes updated throttle actuators and a comprehensive cooling system refresh. The exterior and interior show honest wear expected of a well-maintained driver's car, but the powertrain and subframe remain in excellent functional order, providing a pure, analog driving experience.",
