    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW 540i xDrive, finished in a stunning Mineral White Metallic over a rich Cognac Dakota leather interior. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between executive luxury and athletic performance. The exterior presents very well with a deep, mirror-like finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, professional touch-up on the rear quarter panel. The 19-inch alloy wheels are wrapped in Continental tires with plenty of tread remaining, though one wheel shows light curb rash. Under the hood, the 3.0L B58 inline-six engine is smooth and powerful, backed by a full service history from BMW authorized centers. The interior remains a highlight; the leather is supple and clean, with only light wear visible on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All premium features, including the high-resolution navigation system, Harman Kardon audio, and multi-zone climate control, are in perfect working order. This car has been smoke-free and garage-kept, offering a refined driving experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
