    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really great shape and has been super well-loved, making it the perfect pick if you're looking for something reliable that still looks sharp on the road. It\u2019s clean, runs like a dream, and is totally ready for its next big adventure with you! I\u2019ve taken really good care of it over the years, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by and take it for a spin!",
